Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.07,0:03:14.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初吻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.38,0:03:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.81,0:04:01.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.20,0:04:03.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就差那么一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.57,0:04:08.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.88,0:04:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连臀部都越过两米以上的高度了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:13.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经是高校最佳记录了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:14.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.04,0:04:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.64,0:04:26.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是该吃点心的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要开动了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.02,0:04:41.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.10,0:04:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为肚子饿了所以没办法随心所欲的发力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.04,0:04:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真像小夜你的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.82,0:04:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是原因之一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.19,0:04:53.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我总觉得我的身体在抗拒我使出全力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:04:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是没有这些因素的话 你早就去参加国民体育大会了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.60,0:04:59.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.83,0:05:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.87,0:05:03.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你吃那么多东西却完全不会发胖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.37,0:05:04.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢 为什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.98,0:05:09.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还为减肥在烦恼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个令人嫉妒的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:13.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等 等等 香里 便当要翻了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.57,0:05:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.75,0:05:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大的飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.28,0:05:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 是轰炸机吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:34.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轰炸机？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.94,0:05:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,投放炸弹的飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:38.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那架飞机也是要飞去什么地方参加战争吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.78,0:05:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,参加战争？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.01,0:05:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我是听在「基地」工作的妈妈说的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.23,0:05:47.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都会从冲绳出发去参加战争
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:49.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从前也好现在也好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是因为有了「基地」大家才有饭吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.38,0:05:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管妈妈是这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.30,0:05:55.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我还是讨厌这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.72,0:05:59.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.14,0:06:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.40,0:06:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜完全记不起一年以前发生的一切了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不过那架飞机…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:13.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总觉得以前好像也见过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:15.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.86,0:06:18.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该去医院了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊 竟然有凯前辈送你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.90,0:06:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要知道 他很帅啊 对他有兴趣的女孩子多的很呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.55,0:06:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是没怎么见过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:35.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在外头好像就知道打架
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.19,0:06:38.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上一次也是三更半夜受了伤回到家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.51,0:06:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真被他吓死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:41.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你讨厌他？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.85,0:06:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讨厌打架
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.02,0:06:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.23,0:06:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长…他不再打棒球了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.12,0:06:50.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前经常打吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.77,0:06:52.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可是棒球部的前皇牌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:53.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇牌投手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.29,0:06:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一点都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:01.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还要花很多时间吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:02.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:07.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天的运动会 你可别因为睡过头而迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.71,0:07:09.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.52,0:07:19.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一次一次地实在是麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.86,0:07:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 不用介意的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.15,0:07:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去的时候我坐公交车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:24.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.91,0:07:29.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯 听说你以前打棒球？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.57,0:07:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在小夜你来我家之前就不打了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.79,0:07:36.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被爸爸收养 都已经过了一年了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:39.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仍然净是些我一无所知的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.96,0:07:41.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去并不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸不是也这么说了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是家人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.24,0:07:47.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然没有血缘关系 但我们现在是家人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.12,0:07:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:52.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在去医院之前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.54,0:07:55.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就路过一下你喜欢的那片大海吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:07:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.05,0:08:31.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有「实验体」的反应吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.73,0:08:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然已经扩大了搜索范围
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.12,0:08:35.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是还没有任何发现
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.76,0:08:37.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.38,0:08:40.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经尽了全力搜索「实验体」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.34,0:08:44.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我们可以调用的人员也是有限的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一点我希望你可以理解 先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:51.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,班?阿尔加诺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.95,0:08:56.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然你可能不想听从 我这个年龄和你儿子相仿的人所说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.21,0:09:00.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我所说的话 同时也代表了你上司想说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.79,0:09:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 会让两只「实验体」逃脱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是你们的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.01,0:09:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.62,0:09:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样最好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.52,0:09:13.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 「B型」现在大概在哪一块区域？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.49,0:09:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕 是在古座
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.23,0:09:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古座？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:22.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲绳市吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:27.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs23\bord1}下一条新闻是有关在名护市发生的 连续路过杀人事件的追踪报道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.18,0:09:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs23\bord1}根据警方的调查
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.08,0:09:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs23\bord1}虽然看上去犯人像是用锐利的刃具 袭击女被害者并将其杀害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.10,0:09:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs23\bord1}但是从发现遗体的现场却几乎没留下任何血迹来看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.81,0:09:42.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs23\bord1}应该是在其他地方将被害者杀害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.65,0:09:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音无小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.66,0:09:44.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs23\bord1}再将其搬运到现场
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:44.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.72,0:09:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs23\bord1}警方已经宣布将会全力追查此案
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.33,0:09:47.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你感觉怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想起什么来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.62,0:09:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs23\bord1}好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.70,0:09:52.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.70,0:09:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs23\bord1}现在来说一些有季节性的话题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs23\bord1}上一个周末 做为惯例所举办的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:57.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 在点滴结束之前 你就好好的静养一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.06,0:09:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs23\bord1}古座圣殿祭典顺利开幕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:09:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:10:03.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs23\bord1}许多人携带家人一起前来参加 今年已经是第13次举办的圣殿祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.89,0:10:06.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs23\bord1}起用了许多街头艺人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.65,0:10:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记忆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.69,0:10:08.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也只能顺其自然了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.11,0:10:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs23\bord1}以及应用了最新的设备…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:12.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么了？ 真不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.67,0:11:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:47.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 搞什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女孩子 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.43,0:11:53.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出了什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.12,0:11:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.53,0:11:54.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.60,0:12:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 就像这样心想着颈部与肩膀是互相连着的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.15,0:12:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不想也是连着的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像这样 感觉像是将球推向想要投的位置一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.48,0:12:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要投到这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.67,0:12:22.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去问球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:28.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 公园里可是禁止做投球练习的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.05,0:12:30.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜姐姐 欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.03,0:12:31.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.64,0:12:34.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为一个人都没有 不知不觉就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:38.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸你啊…就算没有人也不行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.41,0:12:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好难接的线路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜 把空饭盒拿出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.31,0:12:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我自己会洗的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:51.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我浸一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.77,0:12:54.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 发生什么事了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.36,0:12:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 只是我心血来潮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.43,0:12:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心血来潮想要孝顺父母么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:01.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 比赛用的鞋不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:03.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又忘东西了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.35,0:13:05.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在社团活动的房间里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 应该是在那棵树下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.12,0:13:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去学校跑一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在去？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.76,0:13:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天早上开始就要开运动会了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,30分钟 30分钟就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先别吃晚饭 记得要等我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:18.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不能先吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.04,0:13:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了啦 记得别跑太快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.56,0:13:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种话是应该对高中生说的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:27.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有29分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.68,0:13:30.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐别摔倒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.07,0:13:31.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会摔倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.27,0:13:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 欢迎 戴比特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.82,0:13:45.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你找我的女儿有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戴比特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.29,0:13:49.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有事情要和你谈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:52.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里克 你上楼去看电视吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.00,0:13:53.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.53,0:13:55.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.83,0:13:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是要去拿遗忘的东西嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.14,0:13:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去快回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.05,0:14:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.05,0:14:20.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「组织」将小夜托付给你已经快一年了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.85,0:14:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她没有出现变化吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.48,0:14:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有 我也不会把她交给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.70,0:14:26.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.88,0:14:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你死去的女儿的替代品吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.37,0:14:36.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是本月的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.33,0:14:52.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然关大门了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.58,0:14:54.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于 见到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.55,0:15:59.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.36,0:16:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.62,0:16:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人都没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:16.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 他确实拿着像小刀似的凶器
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:19.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个一定是杀害女孩子的杀人魔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.01,0:16:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是通知警察比较…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.56,0:16:31.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.31,0:16:35.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.25,0:16:41.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.37,0:17:11.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「charlie」呼叫「bravo」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由C5至C7
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.16,0:17:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认到「实验体jerry」的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.19,0:17:16.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再从空中确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:18.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白 立刻派战斗直升机赶赴现场
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.13,0:17:39.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.42,0:17:40.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.24,0:17:43.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事吗 香里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.92,0:17:45.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 这是小夜的鞋子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.50,0:17:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她忘了拿了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.72,0:17:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 小夜那家伙已经跑去学校拿了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.84,0:17:56.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛啊 老爸 现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.98,0:17:59.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.19,0:18:02.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就快点给小夜买个手机嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.72,0:18:05.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 好麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.82,0:18:06.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.50,0:18:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.18,0:18:57.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.04,0:19:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一阵一阵的疼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.90,0:19:29.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到底是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:30.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「翼手」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.74,0:19:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「翼手」？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.98,0:19:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸食鲜血的禽兽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:38.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会吸血吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.69,0:20:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.18,0:20:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.39,0:20:17.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.40,0:20:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.57,0:20:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.18,0:20:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.57,0:21:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.80,0:21:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.77,0:21:16.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜 与它战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.08,0:21:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.08,0:23:30.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜 和它战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.14,0:23:33.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人轻声说道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.69,0:23:35.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在与他接吻的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.56,0:23:37.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从口中流入的鲜血
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.32,0:23:40.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我重新在战场上翩翩起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.36,0:23:43.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将要变了 我就要开始改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.22,0:23:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手中的利刃 催促着我去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.76,0:23:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一集 BLOOD＋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.65,0:23:51.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.17,0:23:54.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我 凯
